<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Eventos</title>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/8c7b135ad9.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/eventos.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
           <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-12 logo">
             <a href="/"><img src="images/COMIDITA.jpg" alt=></a>
           </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-2 navegacion">
            <ul>
              <li><a href="/">Volver</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>                       
         </div>
     </header>
     <section class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <article class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10">
            <h1>Eventos</h1>
            <p>En Comidita contamos con eventos. Contactanos para enterarte de las promociones
                y mucho más. Completa el formulario y en la brevedad nos estaremos contactando. 
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
     </section>
     <section class="container">
       <div class="row">
         <form action="" method="POST" class="col-10 col-md-8 col-lg-6">

          <label for="">Nombre</label> <br>   
          <input type="text" name="" id="" placeholder="Juan" required="true"><br>
          
          <label for="">Apellido</label><br>
          <input type="text" name="" id="" placeholder="Martinez" required="true"><br>

          <label for="">Telefono</label><br>
          <input type="number" name="" id="" placeholder="1234467825" required="true"><br>

          <label for="">Email</label><br>
          <input type="email" name="" id="" placeholder="comidita@gmail.com" required="true"><br>

          <span>Dia</span>
          <select name="dia" id="">
            <option value="lunes">Lunes</option>
            <option value="marts">Martes</option>
            <option value="miercoles">Miercoles</option>
            <option value="jueves">Jueves</option>
            <option value="viernes">Viernes</option>
            <option value="sabado">Sabado</option>
            <option value="domingo">Domingo</option>
          </select>
          <div class="radio">
            <label for="">Mañana</label>
            <input type="radio" name="" id="mañana">
            <label for="">Tarde</label>
            <input type="radio" name="" id="tarde">
            <label for="">Noche</label>
            <input type="radio" name="" id="noche"><br>
          </div>
          <span>¿Horario que desea llegar?</span>
          <select name="horario">
            <option value="9">9hs</option>
            <option value="10">10hs</option>
            <option value="11">11hs</option>
            <option value="12">12hs</option>
            <option value="13">13hs</option>
            <option value="14">14hs</option>
            <option value="15">15hs</option>
            <option value="16">16hs</option>
            <option value="17">17hs</option>
            <option value="18">18hs</option>
            <option value="19">19hs</option>
            <option value="20">20hs</option>
            <option value="21">21hs</option>
            <option value="22">22hs</option>
          </select> <br>

          <span>dejanos un comentario</span><br>
          <textarea name="" id="" cols="10" rows="5"></textarea><br>

          <div>
            <button type="submit">Enviar</button>
            <button type="reset">Cancelar</button> 
          </div>
          
         </form>
       </div>
     </section>

     <footer id="footer" class="container-fluid">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-10 contacto">
            <h3>Contacto</h3>
            <p>Telefono: 1234567890</p>
            <p>Email: comidita@gmail.com</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-10 order">
            <img src="images/COMIDITA.jpg" alt="">
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-10 redes">
            <a href="" class="facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-square"></i></a>
            <a href="" class="instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram-square"></i></a>
            <a href="" class="twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </footer> 



     <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>